<div class="row">
  <div class="col s12 m6">
    {{#md-card title="Step 1:"}}
      {{#md-card-content}}
        You sign up and we drop off a clean bucket with a fresh compostable
        liner and lid.
        <br>
        <br>
        <img alt="Bucket"
             class="responsive-img"
             src="/assets/images/step_1.png"
             title="we deliver your bucket to you">
      {{/md-card-content}}
    {{/md-card}}
  </div>

  <div class="col s12 m6">
    {{#md-card title="Step 2:"}}
      {{#md-card-content}}
        You fill the bucket with compostable waste (food scraps, certified
        compostable serviceware, and other organic materials).
        <img alt="Bucket"
             class="responsive-img"
             src="/assets/images/step_2.png"
             title="food scraps, serviceware, a liner to keep your bucket clean">
      {{/md-card-content}}
    {{/md-card}}
  </div>

  <div class="col s12 m6">
    {{#md-card title="Step 3:"}}
      {{#md-card-content}}
        You leave the bucket out on pick-up day; we replace it with a cleaned
        bucket, fresh liner, and lid.
        <br>
        <br>
        <img alt="Bucket"
             class="responsive-img"
             src="/assets/images/step_3_1.jpg"
             title="we'll replace your bucket on pick-up day">
      {{/md-card-content}}
    {{/md-card}}
  </div>

  <div class="col s12 m6">
    {{#md-card title="Step 4:"}}
      {{#md-card-content}}
        Your waste is transformed into premium, locally-sourced, black gold,
        otherwise known as compost.
        <br>
        <br>
        <img alt="Bucket"
             class="responsive-img"
             src="/assets/images/step_4.jpg"
             title="let the composting begin">

      {{/md-card-content}}
    {{/md-card}}
  </div>

  <div class="col s12 m6">
    {{#md-card title="Step 5:" class="center-align"}}
      {{#md-card-content}}
        The compost gets distributed to community gardens, urban agriculture,
        or back to you.
        <br>
        <br>
        <img alt="Bucket"
             class="responsive-img"
             src="/assets/images/step_5_1.jpg"
             title="when the black gold is ready, we help redistribute it back to the earth">
      {{/md-card-content}}
    {{/md-card}}
  </div>
</div>

